channel.title: Tune 2.4 Blue Oyster Club Mix - by thomasonline [nutterHouse, EDM]
channel.description:
[https://soundcloud.com/thomasonline-633982140/tune-2-4-bule-oyster-club-1](https://soundcloud.com/thomasonline-633982140/tune-2-4-bule-oyster-club-1)
Tune 2.4 (Bule Oyster Club Mix) Made with Auxy. Rewritten beats, bass, piano and Hammond organs. Bass form RAC essentials, Hammond vintage keys and piano, with few classic Auxy sounds. No loops has been used, written from the scratch note by note. **contact: hello@thomasonline.pl**
[![label|500x500](upload://9YW8Gu2HgxutAujmJOrBM1aR58J.jpeg)](https://soundcloud.com/thomasonline-633982140/tune-2-4-bule-oyster-club-mix)
Enjoy!
